Class TaggingCoreItemQueryDefinition<R,I extends TimelineQueryParameters>

  • Type Parameters:
    I - The valid instance class
    R - Typte of the results of this query.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractNoteQuery, AbstractTagQuery, AbstractUserTaggingCoreQuery, TaggingCoreItemTimeLimitsQuery, UserTaggedBlogQuery, UserTaggingCoreQuery

    public abstract class TaggingCoreItemQueryDefinition<R,I extends TimelineQueryParameters>
extends AbstractUserQuery<R,I>
    The TaggingCoreItemQueryDefinition is the base QueryDefinition for all tagging items such as Tag, UserTaggedResource. Attention: This class must be thread safe.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
